msgid ""
"This indicates that the interrupt is served only by CPU7. Shutting down CPU7 "
"does not migrate the interrupt to another CPU::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../core-api/irq/managed_irq.rst:83
msgid ""
"This can be verified via the debugfs interface (/sys/kernel/debug/irq/"
"irqs/48). The dstate field will include IRQD_IRQ_DISABLED, IRQD_IRQ_MASKED "
"and IRQD_MANAGED_SHUTDOWN."
