#: ../../../core-api/irq/managed_irq.rst:108
msgid ""
"Interrupt 48 is now served on CPU6 because the system avoids CPUs 4, 5 and "
"7. If CPU6 is taken offline, the interrupt migrates to one of the "
"\"isolated\" CPUs::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../core-api/irq/managed_irq.rst:115
msgid ""
"The interrupt is shut down once all CPUs listed in its smp_affinity mask are "
"offline."
msgstr ""
